har_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"有人告诉过我，只可惜那时我忽然忘了。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"原来你也是个很冲动的人。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"为了什么呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"我看不惯他们欺负人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"他们欺负谁了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"是个……是个女人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"我也想到一定是个女人……是不是长得很美？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":348,"line_end":348},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"长得倒还不难看。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":350,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"叫什么名字？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"她自己说她叫花夜来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"连见都没有见过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"他们也根本没有让我说话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"然后呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"然后她就一定要请我喝酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"你是不是喝了很多？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":372,"line_end":372},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"不太少。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":2,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"然后呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"然后……然后我就走了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"就这么简单？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"难道你没有吃什么亏？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"那倒没有。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"看来你若不是很聪明，就一定是运气很不错。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"你跟她分手之后，就遇见了乔老三？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":400,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"那时天刚亮。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"那时你还不知道他是个什么样的人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":404,"line_end":404},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"那时你在他的船上？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":410,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"现在那条船已沉了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":412,"line_end":412},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"但你却一点也看不出像下过水的样子。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"船沉了下去，我并没有沉下去。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":416,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"也许这只因为你运气不好。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我不懂。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":428,"line_end":428},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"你也没听说过'僧王'铁水这个人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":432,"line_end":432},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"看来这人不但是个怪物，而且胆子也不小。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":438,"line_end":438},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"他竟敢公然反抗少林派，武功当然也很高。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":444,"line_end":444},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"想必也就是因为这缘故，他才会脱离少林的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":450,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"她叹了口气，接着道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你说的方刚，是不是那位练过金钟罩、铁布衫的前辈？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我打的那四个和尚，莫非就是他的门下？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":468,"line_end":468},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"她又叹口气道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"何况这件事错的并不是他，是你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":478,"line_end":478},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"是我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":480,"line_end":480},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"看来我想不认错也不行了。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"我可以解释。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":492,"line_end":492},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"你难道已忘了，他通常是个很不讲理的人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":494,"line_end":494},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"所以我除了被他打死之外，已没有别的路可走了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"也许你还有一条路可走。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"哪条路？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":500,"line_end":500},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"顾道人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"道人还在高卧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":510,"line_end":510},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"他从昨天一直赌到现在，根本还没有睡。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":512,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"道人的豪兴倒不浅。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我现在可以进去找他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":520,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"乔老三的朋友，就是我们的朋友，你随时都可去进去，只不过……","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":522,"line_end":522},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我可以在旁边等，看人赌钱也是件很有趣的事。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"你好像对什么事都很有兴趣。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你放心，就算有人要卖我，只怕也没有人肯买。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":536,"line_end":536},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"华华凤","listener":null,"text":"这句话也没有说错，又有谁肯买个呆子呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":538,"line_end":538},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"华华凤","listener":null,"text":"我真的像是个呆子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你真要进去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我本来就是为了拜访顾道人而来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":544,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"华华凤","listener":null,"text":"别人无论说什么，你全都相信？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":546,"line_end":546},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"华华凤","listener":null,"text":"你若不相信别人，别人又怎么会相信你？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":548,"line_end":548},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"好，你要去就去吧。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":550,"line_end":550},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"你不去拉住她？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"一个女人若真的要走，谁也拉不住的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":564,"line_end":564},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"也许她并不是真的要走呢。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":566,"line_end":566},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"若不是真的要走，我又何必去拉她？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":568,"line_end":568},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"现在我只希望我真的很有运气。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"但我还是要劝你一件事。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":576,"line_end":576},{"speaker":"char_zhu_zhu","speaker_name":"女道士","listener":null,"text":"我在听。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":578,"line_end":578},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"顾道人","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":626,"line_end":626},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"虬髯大汉","listener":null,"text":"现在谈什么输赢？芝翁莫非想收手了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":642,"line_end":642},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"虬髯大汉","listener":null,"text":"现在就收怎么行，我已输了十几文钱了。","tone":"焦急","chapter":2,"line_start":662,"line_end":662},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"虬髯大汉","listener":null,"text":"不","tone":"愤怒","chapter":2,"line_start":672,"line_end":672},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"想到这里，段玉就笑了笑，道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":680,"line_end":680},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"虬髯大汉","listener":null,"text":"还是这位朋友够意思。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":684,"line_end":684},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"不错，我是中原人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":690,"line_end":690},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"贵姓？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":692,"line_end":692},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"姓段，叫段玉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":694,"line_end":694},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"段朋友就押天门如何？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":696,"line_end":696},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"行。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":698,"line_end":698},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我身上还带着些。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":706,"line_end":706},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"幸会得很。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":724,"line_end":724},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"没关系。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":753,"line_end":753},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"僧王","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":757,"line_end":757},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"老弟，一下子何必押这么多呢，还是留着慢慢赌吧。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":2,"line_start":775,"line_end":775},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"没关系。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":777,"line_end":777},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"好，老弟，你真有种。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":779,"line_end":779},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"你真押这么多？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":789,"line_end":789},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"就这么多。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":791,"line_end":791},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你不推了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":797,"line_end":797},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"今天算我认输了。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":799,"line_end":799},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"现在就收了也好，我请三位喝两杯。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":803,"line_end":803},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"这……这怎么敢当。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":809,"line_end":809},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"你先算算赢了多少？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":827,"line_end":827},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"不必算了。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":829,"line_end":829},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":837,"line_end":837},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"这太多了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":839,"line_end":839},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"你以后一定会有很多朋友的……","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":845,"line_end":845},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"改天有空，务必要请到'赛云庄'来聊聊。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":851,"line_end":851},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"我看老弟你想必就是段飞熊段老爷子的大少爷。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":857,"line_end":857},{"speaker":"char_duan_fei_xiong","speaker_name":"段老爷子","listener":null,"text":"对了，除了段家的公子，谁有这么大的出手？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":859,"line_end":859},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"剩下的这十个筹码，不知段公子是要兑什么呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":869,"line_end":869},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"随便。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":871,"line_end":871},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"用赤金来兑行不行？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":873,"line_end":873},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"随便。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":875,"line_end":875},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"王飞","listener":null,"text":"何况这些钱本就是赢来的，花光了也无妨。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":925,"line_end":925},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"这一万两银子我也不能收。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":931,"line_end":931},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":933,"line_end":933},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"他不让别人开口，很快地接着又道：","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":937,"line_end":937},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"但你现在并没有输。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":941,"line_end":941},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"既然输不起，赢了就不能拿。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":943,"line_end":943},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"你若不说，也没有人知道你输不起。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":945,"line_end":945},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":957,"line_end":957},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"这些银子是不是偷来的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":967,"line_end":967},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":969,"line_end":969},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"我们赌得有没有假？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":975,"line_end":975},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我……我……","tone":"焦急","chapter":2,"line_start":985,"line_end":985},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"世上的确再也没有什么比这种运气更好的事了。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":995,"line_end":995},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"世上有这种好运气的人也并不多。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":997,"line_end":997},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"可是我……","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1003,"line_end":1003},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"他红着脸苦笑道：","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1011,"line_end":1011},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"不懂得花钱的男人，一定是个没用的男人。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1023,"line_end":1023},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"因为你一定要先懂得花，才会懂得怎么去赚。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1025,"line_end":1025},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我保证以后一定会用心去学的。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1027,"line_end":1027},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我相信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1033,"line_end":1033},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你本不是来赌钱的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1035,"line_end":1035},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"不是。","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1037,"line_end":1037},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"那么，你是不是有了麻烦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1039,"line_end":1039},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"前辈怎么知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1041,"line_end":1041},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"若不是有了麻烦，谁会来找这邋遢道人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1043,"line_end":1043},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"你也许还不知道这个人的来头。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1049,"line_end":1049},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"请教。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1051,"line_end":1051},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"久闻大名了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1057,"line_end":1057},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"他就是霹雳堂现任的堂主，江湖人称霹雳火。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1059,"line_end":1059},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"其实，我只不过在无意中得罪了一个人。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1065,"line_end":1065},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"得罪了谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1067,"line_end":1067},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"听说他叫做'僧王'铁水。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1069,"line_end":1069},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你怎么得罪他的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1071,"line_end":1071},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"也是为了一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1073,"line_end":1073},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"为了谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1075,"line_end":1075},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"听说她叫做花夜来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1077,"line_end":1077},{"speaker":"char_hua_ye_lai","speaker_name":"花夜来","listener":null,"text":"是不是那女贼花夜来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1079,"line_end":1079},{"speaker":"char_hua_ye_lai","speaker_name":"花夜来","listener":null,"text":"大概是的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1081,"line_end":1081},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"她跟你有什么关系？是你的什么人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1083,"line_end":1083},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我根本不认得她。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1085,"line_end":1085},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"但你却不惜为了她而得罪了僧王铁水。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1087,"line_end":1087},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我根本也不知道那四个和尚是他的徒弟。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1089,"line_end":1089},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"四个和尚？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1091,"line_end":1091},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"王飞","listener":null,"text":"所以你不分青红皂白，就去打抱不平了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1097,"line_end":1097},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"他是为了我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1113,"line_end":1113},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我有个儿子，叫卢子云。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":2,"line_start":1117,"line_end":1117},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我听说过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1119,"line_end":1119},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"哦，你一向在中原，怎么会听说过他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1121,"line_end":1121},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1135,"line_end":1135},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"但他到了杭州之后，却突然间失踪了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1137,"line_end":1137},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"失踪了？前辈怎么知道他失踪了呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1139,"line_end":1139},{"speaker":"char_hua_ye_lai","speaker_name":"花夜来","listener":null,"text":"他又咳嗽了几声，才接着道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1143,"line_end":1143},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"铁水叫人去找花夜来，为的就是要追问令郎的下落？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1147,"line_end":1147},{"speaker":"char_hua_ye_lai","speaker_name":"花夜来","listener":null,"text":"不错。","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1149,"line_end":1149},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你可知道我为什么要到这里来找顾道人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1153,"line_end":1153},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"不是为了赌钱？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1155,"line_end":1155},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"除了赌钱外，还有一个更大的原因。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1157,"line_end":1157},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"什么原因？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1159,"line_end":1159},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"为了找你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1161,"line_end":1161},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"所以你就来找我打听这少年的行踪来历？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1169,"line_end":1169},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"这一带地面上的事，还有谁比你更清楚的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1171,"line_end":1171},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"但你为什么一直投有开口呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1173,"line_end":1173},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"想不到赌钱也有好处的。","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1187,"line_end":1187},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1191,"line_end":1191},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"这四天来，前辈一直没有找到花夜来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1193,"line_end":1193},{"speaker":"char_hua_ye_lai","speaker_name":"花夜来","listener":null,"text":"她行踪本就一向很飘忽，否则又怎能活到现在。","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":1195,"line_end":1195},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"但昨天她却忽然出现了。","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":1197,"line_end":1197},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"就连我都从未想到，这女贼居然也敢去游湖。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1199,"line_end":1199},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"昨天我刚来，她就出现了，这倒实在巧得很。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1201,"line_end":1201},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"天下凑巧的事本就很多。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1203,"line_end":1203},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"也许这就叫无巧不成书。","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1205,"line_end":1205},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"直到现在为止，卢公子还是连一点消息都没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1207,"line_end":1207},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"完全没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1209,"line_end":1209},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"所以这件事还是没有解决。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1211,"line_end":1211},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"他笑了笑，接着道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1215,"line_end":1215},{"speaker":"char_wang_fei","speaker_name":"王飞","listener":null,"text":"不错，你至少应该替卢九爷找出花夜来这女贼来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1223,"line_end":1223},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九爷","listener":null,"text":"昨天晚上，我的确是跟她在一起的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1225,"line_end":1225},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"在什么地方？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1227,"line_end":1227},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"在湖边一栋小房子里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1229,"line_end":1229},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"现在你还能不能找到那地方？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1231,"line_end":1231},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我可以去试试看。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1233,"line_end":1233},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我们现在就去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1235,"line_end":1235},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"这是哪里来的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1243,"line_end":1243},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"在一个花盆里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1245,"line_end":1245},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"在花盆里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1247,"line_end":1247},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"他叹息着，又道：","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":1253,"line_end":1253},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1257,"line_end":1257},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我就是在这里遇见乔三爷的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1265,"line_end":1265},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"你见过乔三？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1267,"line_end":1267},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"若不是他的指点，我又怎么会找到顾道人那里去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1269,"line_end":1269},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"想不到他居然对你不错，这人脾气一向很古怪的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1271,"line_end":1271},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"这点我倒也同意，本来他几乎要把我淹死的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1273,"line_end":1273},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"但他又怎么会知道这件事的呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1279,"line_end":1279},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"这一带湖面上的事，他不知道的很少。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1281,"line_end":1281},{"speaker":"char_gu_dao_ren","speaker_name":"顾道人","listener":null,"text":"龙是不敢当的，只不过是两条地头蛇而已。","tone":"大笑","chapter":2,"line_start":1287,"line_end":1287},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"我还是走了一段路。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1293,"line_end":1293},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"走了多久？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1295,"line_end":1295},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","listener":null,"text":"你走得快不快？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":1301,"line_end":1301},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"也不快，那时……那时我正想着心事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1303,"line_end":1303},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"这样说来，那屋子离这里一定并不太远。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1305,"line_end":1305},{"speaker":"char_duan_yu","speaker_name":"段玉","listener":null,"text":"好像是不太远。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":1307,"line_end":1307},{"speaker":"char_lu_jiu","speaker_name":"卢九","li